<div class=3D"outline-text-2" id=3D"text-8">
<p>
Archive: <a href=3D"https://discuss.ocaml.org/t/ann-opam-2-6-0-alpha1/18372=
/1">https://discuss.ocaml.org/t/ann-opam-2-6-0-alpha1/18372/1</a>
